# Spectral Design System

## Brand Identity
Dark military intelligence aesthetic. Think: **Mission Operations Centre meets classified briefing room**. Not Silicon Valley, not government GIS portal. Credible, tense, data-dense.

## Colour Tokens (Tailwind config)

### Foundation
| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `bg-spectral-bg` | `#0A0A0F` | Primary page background |
| `bg-spectral-surf1` | `#0F0F1A` | Card / panel surface |
| `bg-spectral-surf2` | `#14141F` | Nested panel, hover state |
| `bg-spectral-surf3` | `#1A1A2E` | Deepest panel, modal overlay |
| `text-spectral-primary` | `#F5F5F5` | Body copy, headings |
| `text-spectral-secondary` | `#9CA3AF` | Labels, metadata, captions |
| `text-spectral-muted` | `#6B7280` | Disabled, footnotes |
| `border-spectral-divider` | `#1E1E2E` | Hairlines, dividers |

