## Typography
- **Display / headings**: `font-display` (JetBrains Mono) — all data values, coordinates, frequencies, ranges
- **Body**: `font-sans` (Inter or system-ui) — prose, labels, descriptions
- **Mono data**: `font-mono` (JetBrains Mono) — ALWAYS use for: ranges in km, altitudes in ft/m, frequencies in MHz/GHz, coordinates, speed in kts/km/h, ID codes, hex values, timestamps

## Jammer Tier Badges
Three tiers with distinct visual treatment:
```tsx
// tier_1_military — solid red outline
<span className="tier-badge tier-1">TIER 1 MIL</span>

// tier_2_sdr — amber outline
<span className="tier-badge tier-2">TIER 2 SDR</span>

// tier_3_cots — muted grey outline
<span className="tier-badge tier-3">TIER 3 COTS</span>
```
CSS classes are in `app/globals.css`.

## Classification Banner
Top of every page layout. Fixed position. Full-width.
```tsx
<div className="classification-banner">
  UNCLASSIFIED // FOR OFFICIAL TRAINING USE ONLY
</div>
```
Background: `#1a1a00`, text: `#ffd700`, border-bottom: `1px solid #ffd700`.
Font: JetBrains Mono, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.1em.

## Component Patterns

### Module Card (Dashboard)
```tsx
<div className="rounded-lg border border-spectral-divider bg-spectral-surf1 p-6 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
  <div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
    <Icon className="h-5 w-5 text-purple-400" />
    <h3 className="text-spectral-primary font-semibold">{title}</h3>
  </div>
  <p className="text-spectral-secondary text-sm">{description}</p>
</div>
```

### Data Value Display
Always JetBrains Mono for numbers:
```tsx
<span className="font-mono text-spec-gnss">1575.42 MHz</span>
<span className="font-mono text-spectral-primary">850 km/h</span>
<span className="font-mono text-status-red">JAMMED</span>
```

### Stat Card
```tsx
<div className="bg-spectral-surf1 border border-spectral-divider rounded p-4">
  <p className="text-spectral-secondary text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">{label}</p>
  <p className="font-mono text-2xl text-spectral-primary mt-1">{value}</p>
</div>
```

## Anti-patterns — NEVER DO THESE
- No white or light backgrounds anywhere in the app
- No generic blue buttons (use `purple-600` or `spectral-accent` for primary actions)
- No default Tailwind colours without spectral prefix where spectral tokens exist
- No `text-gray-*` — use `text-spectral-secondary` or `text-spectral-muted`
- No inline styles for colours — use Tailwind tokens only
- No emoji in UI (unless a deliberate status indicator)
- Classification banner must never be hidden, overflowed, or obscured
